  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will measure the efficacy and safety of an early postoperative anticoagulation
      self-management program, using the CoaguChek S device, in patients undergoing mechanical
      valve replacements. Patients will be randomized into a study group (self-management) or a
      control group (physician management).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
